radio_info.short: RTV Emmen is the local broadcaster for Southeast Drenthe. On weekdays they offer a mix of current affairs programs and non-stop music. Monday / Saturday
radio_info.rest:
you start from 8 to 9 Morning your day with Morning Edition, which includes the local headlines and local events. Following on Morning Edition there every day Afternoon Edition. In the evenings houses their target programs. With this they offer a range of programs for every resident of Southeast Drenthe: From Country to youth programs, from Gospel to chart.
